用的接码平台本来就是一次性的，现在又不能修改手机号重新验证", "last_modified": 1780077825, "replies": 27, "id": 1216598}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_large.png?m=1751736785", "name": "openai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_normal.png?m=1751736785", "title": "OpenAI", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/openai", "topics": 3945, "footer": "", "header": "关于 OpenAI 旗下产品 GPT，DALL·E，和 ChatGPT 的讨论。请不要在 V2EX 的回复中粘贴复制来自 AI 生成的文本。", "title_alternative": "OpenAI", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_mini.png?m=1751736785", "stars": 3104, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1135, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 663321, "username": "Achao1121", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Achao1121", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47f6/f490/663321_mini.png?m=1704094324", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47f6/f490/663321_normal.png?m=1704094324", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47f6/f490/663321_large.png?m=1704094324", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47f6/f490/663321_xlarge.png?m=1704094324", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47f6/f490/663321_xxlarge.png?m=1704094324", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47f6/f490/663321_xxxlarge.png?m=1704094324", "created": 1700358716, "last_modified": 1704094324, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "wendy12478", "last_touched": 1780110503, "title": "电话号码怎么解决？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216568", "created": 1780063213, "deleted": 0, "content": "已经试了很多接码平台了，搞不定怎么办各位大神？", "content_rendered": "<p>已经试了很多接码平台了，搞不定怎么办各位大神？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780063213, "replies": 24, "id": 1216568}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23470, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3684, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 526487, "username": "Carver9527", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Carver9527", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d6fcc3fd0f0bbdb22068e4ca8c4822?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d6fcc3fd0f0bbdb22068e4ca8c4822?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d6fcc3fd0f0bbdb22068e4ca8c4822?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1609568610, "last_modified": 1609568610, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "revalue", "last_touched": 1780139167, "title": "开发转运维，是否是一条不归路", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216610", "created": 1780104963, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：二本 Go 开发，7 年经验，今年 4 月初拿到礼包，没到能够躺平的水平。\r\n\r\n开始投简历，准备找下一份工作。中间经过一些波折，最终收获了一份运维开发的 offer 。期间因为一直没有合适的机会，整个人都焦虑了。\r\n\r\n入职几天，发现主要是做运维的工作，而且需要值班，强度一下被拉高了，怀疑自己是不是走上了一条不归路。", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：二本 Go 开发，7 年经验，今年 4 月初拿到礼包，没到能够躺平的水平。</p>\n<p>开始投简历，准备找下一份工作。中间经过一些波折，最终收获了一份运维开发的 offer 。期间因为一直没有合适的机会，整个人都焦虑了。</p>\n<p>入职几天，发现主要是做运维的工作，而且需要值班，强度一下被拉高了，怀疑自己是不是走上了一条不归路。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780106507, "replies": 22, "id": 1216610}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1754172750", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1754172750", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 12862, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1754172750", "stars": 6205, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 624972, "username": "YaNanGe", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/YaNanGe", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_mini.png?m=1730697636", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_normal.png?m=1730697636", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_large.png?m=1730697636", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_xlarge.png?m=1730697636", "created": 1681959737, "last_modified": 1730697636, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "junyee", "last_touched": 1780135268, "title": "有没有大佬知道如何获取安卓唯一标识", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216634", "created": 1780110683, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，公司自己内部使用的 APP ，不需要上架商店，扫码安装。\r\n\r\n系统为 11 、12 。设备需要经常刷机。\r\n\r\n在不 root ，不通过电脑单独开启某权限的情况下如何获取不会改变的唯一编码？", "content_rendered": "如题，公司自己内部使用的 APP ，不需要上架商店，扫码安装。<br /><br />系统为 11 、12 。设备需要经常刷机。<br /><br />在不 root ，不通过电脑单独开启某权限的情况下如何获取不会改变的唯一编码？", "last_modified": 1780130668, "replies": 20, "id": 1216634}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1ee3/dfcd/1319_large.png?m=1771929942", "name": "openclaw", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1ee3/dfcd/1319_normal.png?m=1771929942", "title": "OpenClaw", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/openclaw", "topics": 307, "footer": "", "header": "| OpenClaw | 原名 ClawdBot MlotBot |\r\n|---|---|\r\n| 简介 | 支持本地运行与自动任务执行 |\r\n| 官网| https://openclaw.ai/ |\r\n| Moltbook| https://www.moltbook.com |", "title_alternative": "OpenClaw", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1ee3/dfcd/1319_mini.png?m=1771929942", "stars": 293, "founder_id": 69824, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1319, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 649188, "username": "imrockpan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/imrockpan", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad97/4c99/649188_mini.png?m=1695957940", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad97/4c99/649188_normal.png?m=1695957940", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad97/4c99/649188_large.png?m=1695957940", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad97/4c99/649188_xlarge.png?m=1695957940", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad97/4c99/649188_xxlarge.png?m=1695957940", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad97/4c99/649188_xxxlarge.png?m=1695957940", "created": 1695049604, "last_modified": 1695957940, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "qian88199496", "last_touched": 1780099392, "title": "小龙虾为什么突然不火了？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216575", "created": 1780064862, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近发现，以前很火的小龙虾，已经开始不用了。\r\n\r\n有点好奇，你们为什么不再用了呢？\r\n\r\nA. 配置太复杂，折腾半天才能跑起来  \r\nB. 出现了更好的替代品  \r\nC. 担心安全或隐私方面  \r\nD. 太烧 Token ，成本难以接受  \r\nE. 解决不了我的实际问题  \r\nF. 对 AI Agent 已经没兴趣了", "content_rendered": "<p>最近发现，以前很火的小龙虾，已经开始不用了。</p>\n<p>有点好奇，你们为什么不再用了呢？</p>\n<p>A. 配置太复杂，折腾半天才能跑起来<br/>\nB. 出现了更好的替代品<br/>\nC. 担心安全或隐私方面<br/>\nD. 太烧 Token ，成本难以接受<br/>\nE. 解决不了我的实际问题<br/>\nF. 对 AI Agent 已经没兴趣了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780084831, "replies": 19, "id": 1216575}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_large.png?m=1648291973", "name": "reading", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_normal.png?m=1648291973", "title": "阅读", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/reading", "topics": 816, "footer": "", "header": "少上网，多读书", "title_alternative": "Reading", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_mini.png?m=1648291973", "stars": 1718, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 111, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 660849, "username": "chaoziCoder", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/chaoziCoder", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "g